<ab facs="#facs_232_r1l5">die vlman Stromerin <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>ur</ex>gerin</expan> / vnd Görg Stromeir ir ſun <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_232_r1l6"> <expan>B<ex>ur</ex>ger</expan> / vvie daʒ Jr dem <expan cert="unknown">H</expan> Pfeıffer <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Pürheim irem Armman / der </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_232_r1l7"> <expan>hint<ex>er</ex></expan> Jn ſıcʒe vnd den mit tür vnd tor beſlieſſen / ſeıne pferde 
